import AppLayout from './component/AppLayout'
import Head from 'next/head'  //next 에서 head 는 지원해준다.

function profile() {
    return (
        <>
            <Head>
                <title>profile</title>
            </Head>
            <AppLayout>
                프로필
            </AppLayout>
        </>

}


export default profile
